    "data": "اَلسَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكَ يَابْنَ رَسُوْلِ اللهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكَ يَابْنَ اَمِيْرِ الْمُؤْمِنِيْنَ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكَ يَابْنَ سَيِّدَةِ نِسَآءِ الْعَالَمِيْنَ اَشْهَدُ اَنَّكَ قَدْ اَقَمْتَ الصَّلوٰةَ وَ اٰتَيْتَ الزَّکٰوةَ وَ اَمَرْتَ بِالْمَعْرُوْفِ وَ نَهَيْتَ عَنِ الْمُنْكَرِ وَ عَبَدْتَ اللهَ مُخْلِصًا وَ جَاهَدْتَ فِی اللهِ حَقَّ جِهَادِهٖ حَتّٰی اَتٰيكَ الْيَقِيْنُ فَعَلَيْكَ السَّلاَمُ مِنِّیْ مَا بَقِيْتُ وَ بَقِیَ اللَّيْلُ وَالنَّهَارُ وَ عَلٰی اٰلِ بَيْتِكَ الطَّيِّبِيْنَ الطَّاهِرِيْنَ اَنَا يَا مَوْلاَیَ مَوْلًی لَكَ وَ لِآلِ بَيْتِكَ سِلْمٌ لِمَنْ سَالَمَکُمْ وَ حَرْبٌ لِمَنْ حَارَبَکُمْ مُؤْمِنٌ بِسِرِّکُمْ وَ جَهْرِکُمْ وَ ظَاهِرِکُمْ وَ بَاطِنِکُمْ لَعَنَ اللهُ اَعْدَآئَکُمْ مِنَ الْاَوَّلِيْنَ وَ الْاٰخِرِيْنَ وَ اَنَا اَبْرَءُ اِلَی اللهِ تَعَالیٰ مِنْهُمْ يَا مَوْلاَیَ يَا اَبَا مُحَمَّدٍ يَا مَوْلاَیَ يَا اَبَا عَبْدِ اللهِ هٰذَا يَوْمُ الْاِثْنَيْنِ وَ هُوَ يَوْمُکُمَا وَ بِاسْمِکُمَا وَ اَنَا فِيْهِ ضَيْفُکُمَا فَاَضِيْفَانِیْ وَ اَحْسِنَا ضِيَافَتِیْ فَنِعْمَ مَنِ اسْتُضِيْفَ بِهٖ اَنْتُمَا وَ اَنَا فِيْهِ مِنْ جِوَارِکُمَا فَاَجِيْرَانِیْ فَاِنَّکُمَا مَاْمُوْرَانِ بِالضِّيَافَةِ وَ الْاِجَارَةِ فَصَلَّی اللهُ عَلَيْکُمَا وَ آلِکُمَا الطَّيِّبِيْنَ.\nASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YABNA RASOOLIL LAAHE ASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YABNA AMEERIL MOMENEENA ASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YABNA SAYYEDATE NESAAAIL A’ALAMEENA ASH-HADO ANNAKA QAD AQAMTAS SALAATA WA AATAYTAZ ZAKAATA WA AMARTA BIL MA’ROOFE WA NAHAYTA A’NIL MUNKARE WA A’BADTAL LAAHA MUKHLESAN WA JAAHADTA FIL LAAHE HAQQA JEHAADEHI HATTAA ATAAKAL YAQEENO FA A’LAYKAS SALAAMO MINNEE MAA BAQEETO WA BAQEYAL LAYLO WAN NAHAARO WA A’LAA AALE BAYTEKAT TAYYEBEENAT TAAHEREENA ANAA YAA MAWLAAYA MAWLAN LAKA WA LE-AALE BAYTEKA SILMUN LEMAN SAALAMAKUM WA HARBUN LEMAN HAARABAKUM MOMENUN BE SIRREKUM WA JAHREKUM WA ZAAHEREKUM WA BAATENEKUM LA’NAL LAAHO AA’DAAAKUM MENAL AWWALEENA WAL AAKHEREEN WA ANAA ABRAO ELAL LAAHE TA-A’ALAA MINHUM YAA MAWLAAYA YAA ABAA MOHAMMAD YAA MAWLAAYA YAA ABAA A’BDIL LAAHE HAAZAA YAWMUL ISNAYNE WA HOWA YAWMOKOMAA WA BISMEKOMAA WA ANAA FEEHE ZAYFOKOMAA FA-AZEEFAANEE WA AHSENAA ZEYAAFATEE FA-NE’MA MANIS TUZEFA BEHI ANTOMAA WA ANAA FEEHE MIN JEWAAREKOMAA FA AJEERAANEE FA INNAKOMAA MAAMOORAANE BIZ ZEYAAFATE WAL EJAARATE FASALLAL LAAHO A’LAYKOMAA WA AALEKOMAT TAYYEBEENA.\nPeace be on you, O son of the Apostle of Allah! Peace be on you, O son of the Commander of the faithfuls! Peace be on you, O son of the chief of all the women of the worlds! I stand witness that you established prayers, and paid the poor-due, preached goodness, proscribed evil, had sincerely served Allah, strived, leaving no stone unturned, against heavy odds, in the cause of Allah, to the fullest extent, till the inevitable came unto you. So “peace be on you” from me so far I live, and the orbit of “nights following days” call it a day; and on the pure people of your house, I, O my Master, again and again willingly pay allegiance to you, and to your family. I am at peace with him who makes (his) peace with you. I make war against him who goes to war with you. I truly believe in your innermost best aspect, in your evident public role, in your externally appearing style, in your mystical dimensions of spirit. Allah condemns your enemies, those of old, and those of later time. I turn to Allah, the highly praised, breaking all connections with them. O my Master! O Abu Mohammad! (and) O my Master! O Abu Abdullah! Today is Monday, it belongs to both of you, refers to your names, in its hours I take refuge with both of you make me feel at home, a most generous friendly welcome, because whoso turns to you for accommodation lives in ease and comfort, and in this hour it is I who is in your neighborhood, so let me be near you. Verily both of you have been chose and assigned to give asylum and refuge. Blessings of Allah be on you both, and on you pure children.\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    ", 
    "title": "Ziyarah of Imam al Husayn (a) on Monday"
}